entries.femaleVariant: Is this where Gillean Jordan gets fitted out?
Always wondered what it'd feel like to spend a ludicrous amount of eddies on threads.
Then you've come to the right place. Welcome to Jinguji – an oasis of bon goût for those who crave perfection.
Jinguji... Doesn't Gillean Jordan get herself fitted out here?
We try to protect our clients' privacy, buuut... I'd be lyin' if I said no.
The attack didn't scare off customers?
Hey, Zane. Anything new on offer for those of us who "crave perfection."
The attack hasn't scared off your customers?
Always. And especially for those who save my life.
To be honest, our PR have fared well. I announced a new promotion, awarded vouchers to the victims' families...
But in any case, the brand is its own best defense. Some believe I made it all up as a marketing stunt.
And claimed it was a whole squad of cyberpychos who rolled in here. Yeah, heard the radio blurb. Seriously, Zane? "Trained cyberpsychos"?
I admit, the shock following a psycho attack wasn't conducive to "creative" storytelling. But one has to fight for his brand's reputation – in all circumstances.
